3,"uid":171192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:07:02.000Z","msg":"施永青提「聖誕」：X你老母<br />\n<br />\n聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有HardFeeling，《壹週刊》報道，施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我最憎就是聖誕！</span>」</strong>，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23c284223ccf2eb635295476149db64361487ec","tid":1797493,"uid":134497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"661f5b820f0843d73bce36ea01a5fd079af50332","tid":1797493,"uid":59297,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0d0e6cc3e415c56e5010d8f4ae76ad29d51a3a67","tid":1797493,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:59:16.000Z","msg":"上街好多人陪你"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"琴晚出咗啦，仲慘，個個都係一對對發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:13:12.000Z","msg":"正想咁講，知道啲frd出晒去，屌你老味全部都有拖拍咁滯"},{"pid":"14b63a7d36faf731fc5bbe417ec56ee5d8b4d45f","tid":1797493,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"661f5b820f0843d73bce36ea01a5fd079af50332","tid":1797493,"uid":59297,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0d0e6cc3e415c56e5010d8f4ae76ad29d51a3a67","tid":1797493,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:59:16.000Z","msg":"上街好多人陪你"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"琴晚出咗啦，仲慘，個個都係一對對發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T13:17:46.000Z","msg":"搵個仔仔同你一對出去<img src=\"/assets/fac